---

<Layout title="spon.io">
	<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full py-8 self-center flex-1 flex justify-center flex-col px-6">
		<p class="spon mb-6 text-6xl md:text-9xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100 self-start">spon.io</p>
		<p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-500 mb-24">Massive text seems to be popular these days</p>
		<div class="max-w-xl mb-12">
			<div class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">Hello, Iâ€™m Dave. <h1 class="spon inline">Freelance web developer/consultant</h1> based in the <h2 class="spon inline">South West, UK</h2>. With over 10 years of experience in building for the web, <h2 class="inline">I help agencies and SMBs build beautiful websites and apps</h2>.</div>
		</div>
		<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight spon inline-block self-start">Clients:</h3>
